      "content": "The Unity Economy REST API allows you to manage in-game economies including virtual currencies, inventory items, purchases, and player balances. It provides both Admin endpoints for configuring economy resources and Player endpoints for runtime player interactions such as making purchases and checking balances.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Unity Support",
